Goldsmith Tells Sky ‘Inevitable’ Brooks Must Depart News Corp.

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-06T17:52:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/goldsmith-tells-sky-inevitable-brooks-must-depart-news-corp-.html
U.K. lawmaker Zac Goldsmith told Sky
News in an interview that it’s “inevitable” that News
International Chief Executive Officer Rebekah Brooks must step
down as a result of allegations of phone-hacking at the News of
the World newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 